http://linuxcommand.org/wss0030.php#html

ex. 
#!/bin/bash

# make_page - A script to produce an HTML file

cat <<- _EOF_
    <HTML>
    <HEAD>
        <TITLE>
        My System Information
        </TITLE>
    </HEAD>

    <BODY>
    <H1>My System Information</H1>
    </BODY>
    </HTML>
_EOF_


save the file and make sure to make it executable

chmod 700 makepage.pl

then run makepgae.pl >> htmlTest.html

to open the html file created you can use

cygstart.exe htmlTest.html

or to open it in a specific program

cygstart.exe chrome.exe htmlTest.html

